outcome_sumary:
A4NH researchers continued to bring together members from public health, research
organizations, as well as national government
to review current implementation of nutrition sensitive policies through several ongoing platforms, including Transform Nutrition West Africa, the Partnership and Opportunities to Strengthen and Harmonize Actions for Nutrition in India, as well as several Stories of Change initiatives in South Africa, Rwanda, and Nigeria. While COVID-19 related restrictions paused implementation of some nutrition sensitive projects, A4NH researchers and stakeholders from different sectors were still able to convene - often virtually - to design evidence based policies.&nbsp;

